In this piece, we present 10 signs of a potential cheater. As with any behavior, it can be difficult to decipher the intentions behind it.Relatedly, the more symptoms that are present, the likelier it is that a real problem exists.For the victim, this is pretty easy to observe but extraordinarily difficult to accept.Emotional detachment from someone you love is like a punch to the heart. Unfortunately, this disconnection is too often a prelude to relationship deterioration.For a potential cheater, it s easier to distance oneself emotionally from someone than to confront the real problem.It s a cowardly act, in many ways.&nbsp;